summary:
Who is Natalia?

A Polish native speaker, living in the Netherlands for almost 20 years now. Passionate about languages, language backgrounds and interpersonal communication, studied Scandinavian Languages (BA) and General Linguistics (MA) at the UvA. Fluent in Polish, Dutch, English and Swedish; intermediate in Russian and Norwegian.
After finishing the study working at Syngenta with customers and Sales colleagues all over the world. Experienced in export but at the moment focused on customers in Central Europe. 
Aim - developing translation skills.

Proud mother of 2 children: Max of 5 years old and Tomas of 2 years old.
Also interested in foreign cultures, rock music, pets, reading, yoga and beauty.
